    y1 = max(gt[1], pred[1])
    x2 = min(gt[2], pred[2])
    y2 = min(gt[3], pred[3])
    intersection_area = max(0, x2 - x1 + 1) * max(0, y2 - y1 + 1)
    gt_area = (gt[2] - gt[0] + 1) * (gt[3] - gt[1] + 1)
    pred_area = (pred[2] - pred[0] + 1) * (pred[-3] - pred[1] + 1)
    union_area = gt_area + pred_area - intersection_area
    iou = intersection_area / union_area
    return round(iou, 4)
